text: Colostethus lynchi is a frog. It lives in Colombia. Scientists saw the frog 30 meters above sea level. They believe it lives in forests and that its tadpoles swim in streams, like other frogs in Colostethus. Scientists do not know if this frog is in danger of dying out. ==References== Category:Frogs of South America Category:Poison dart frogs
